{"tid":1134202,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"私家車漏油問題","createTime":"2019-05-01T15:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T15:59:41.000Z","uid":174821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8de76b1f1ac9f3acc4923675214f0ee90b5ff4","tid":1134202,"uid":174821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"部十幾年錢七之前跪低左已經整左我幾千，諗住整埋最後一次再壞就劏左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但今日泊咗車聽到幾聲嘀噠聲，望到車底右前方有撻油漬，但等左陣見唔到佢滴落嚟，開車頭睇亦都見唔到明顯漏油地方。因為用泊車sensor，我次次泊差唔多同一個位，所以大概係佢靜止嗰陣時慢慢滴落去<br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴打，呢啲情況其實使唔使即刻拎去整，如果整要大概幾多錢？"},{"pid":"776337a8a81aee1eb23959bdb29e2eb90574b2d0","tid":1134202,"uid":175217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"大佬呀<br />\n你咩款咩年份都唔講<br />\n整車傳心師咩"},{"pid":"efc530fde261f14aa5dc1a9dc6574c17a3f99155","tid":1134202,"uid":208241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:47:25.000Z","msg":"漏油可以喺<br />\n油底漏=冇乜野<br />\nHead gasket=揸多兩揸就tol車"},{"pid":"05a1c89f8171a462bc6be53ee8c841c146612ca5","tid":1134202,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:51:59.000Z","msg":"唔建議整,渣到唔得為止<br />\n漏得多會冧偈<br />\n渣出馬路有危險"},{"pid":"d6360beaafe836830c32a02662a073b75b8a4862","tid":1134202,"uid":174821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"776337a8a81aee1eb23959bdb29e2eb90574b2d0","tid":1134202,"uid":175217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"大佬呀<br />\n你咩款咩年份都唔講<br />\n整車傳心師咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"Sorry巴打，三菱AirTrek 04"},{"pid":"13b378fceceadd03029f095ee67d47360b5724cd","tid":1134202,"uid":174821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05a1c89f8171a462bc6be53ee8c841c146612ca5","tid":1134202,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T15:51:59.000Z","msg":"唔建議整,渣到唔得為止<br />\n漏得多會冧偈<br />\n渣出馬路有危險"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20